quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  29,14,"wlqd 'arsalna nwhana 'iilaa qawmih famakath fihim 'alf sanat 'iilaa khamsin eamana, yadeuhum 'iilaa altwhyd wayanhahum ean alshrk, falam yastajibuu lh, fahlkhm allah baltwfan, wahum zalimun lanfshm bikufrihim wtghyanhm"
  29,15,"fanjyna nwhana wman tabieah mmn kan maeah fi alsfynt, wajaealna dhlk eibratan wezt llealmyn"
  29,16,"wadhkr -ayha alrswl- 'iibrahim ealayh alslam hin daea qwmh: 'ana akhlsu alebadt lilah whdh, wataquu skhth bi'ada' fraydh wajtnab measyh, dhlkm khayr lkm, 'iin kuntum taelamun ma hu khayr lakum mimaa hu sharun lkm"
  29,17,"ma taebudun -ayha alqwm- min dun allah 'iilaa asnamana, wtftrwn kdhbana btsmytkm 'iyaha alht, 'inn awthankm alty tebdwnha min dun allah la tuqadar 'ana trzqkm shyyana, faltamisuu eind allah alrizq la min eind awthankm, wa'akhlasuu lah alebadt walshukr ealaa rizqah 'iyakm, 'iilaa allah turddun min baed mmatkm, fyjazykm ealaa ma emltm"
  29,18,"w'in tkdhdhibu - 'ayuha alnas- rasulina mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wasalam fima daeakum 'iilayh min eibadat allah whdh, faqad kadhabat jamaeat min qablikum rslha fima dethm 'iilayh min alhq, fhl bihim sakhit allh, wama ealaa alrraswl muhamad 'iilaa 'an yblghkm ean allah risalatah albalagh alwadh, waqad faeal"
  29,19,"'awalam yaelam hwla' kayf yunashiy allah alkhalq min aledm, thuma yueiduh min baed fnayh, kama bada'ah 'awal marat khlqana jdydana, la ytedhr ealayh dhlk? 'iina dhlk ealaa allah ysyr, kama kan ysyrana ealayh 'inshawh"
  29,20,"ql -ayha alrswl- lmnkry albaeth baed almmat: siruu fi alard, fanzuruu kayf 'ansha allah alkhlq, walam ytedhr ealayh 'inshawh mbtdaan? fkdhlk la ytedhr ealayh 'iieadat 'inshayh alnash'at alakhr. 'iina allah ealaa kl shay' qdyr, la yejzh shay' aradh"
  29,21,"yedhb man yasha' min khalaqah ealaa ma aslf min jrmh fi 'ayaam hyath, wayarham man yasha' minhum mmn tab waman waeamil salhana, wa'iilayh trjewn, fyjazykm bima emltm"
  29,22,"wma 'antum -ayha alnas- bmejzy allah fi al'ard wala fi alsama' 'iin esytmwh, wama kan lakum min dun allah min wly yali amwrkm, wala nasir yansurukum min allah 'iin 'arad bikum sw'ana"